vg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 27, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xsb1665703008136.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xsb1665703008136.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xsb1665703008136.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xsb1665703008136\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $italic\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"xsb1665703008136___italic_270877\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Apply the italic character attribute to a string in a Unifield.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"xsb1665703008136__topic_d84980e1_d84981e1_d84982e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xsb1665703008136__p_d84983e1_d84984e1_d84985e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$italic</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xsb1665703008136__topic_d56367e1_d56368e1_d56369e1_d56370e1_d56371e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d921063e75\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"xsb1665703008136__table_d8882e1_d8883e1_d8884e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xsb1665703008136__table_d8882e1_d8883e1_d8884e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xsb1665703008136__table_d8882e1_d8883e1_d8884e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xsb1665703008136__table_d8882e1_d8883e1_d8884e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xsb1665703008136__table_d8882e1_d8883e1_d8884e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xsb1665703008136__table_d8882e1_d8883e1_d8884e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xsb1665703008136__table_d8882e1_d8883e1_d8884e1__entry__3\">\n String to italicize\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xsb1665703008136__topic_d56372e1_d56373e1_d56374e1_d56375e1_d56376e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d921063e129\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xsb1665703008136__p_d84992e1_d84993e1_d84994e1\">Returns the result of applying the italic character attribute to <var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xsb1665703008136__topic_d56377e1_d56378e1_d56379e1_d56380e1_d56381e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d921063e141\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xsb1665703008136__d6469e20\">Use in Form components, but only applicable to Unifields.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xsb1665703008136__topic_d56382e1_d56383e1_d56384e1_d56385e1_d56386e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d921063e151\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xsb1665703008136__p_d85004e1_d85005e1_d85006e1\">The function <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$italic</span> returns the result of applying the italic character attribute to <var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var>. The result is visible only in a displayed Unifield.</p>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">MY_UNIFIELD = $italic(\"aaabbb\")</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">Afterwards, MY_UNIFIELD contains aaabbb.</p>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fgf1665702617809.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>stripattributes</a><p>Remove character attributes, frames, and rulers from Source and put the result in Target.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wbm1665703011575.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$stripattributes</a><p>Return the result of removing character attributes, frames, and rulers from a string.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533887\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533887\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$italic Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 27, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $italic Apply the italic character attribute to a string in a Unifield. $italic ( String ) Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description String String String to italicize Return Values Returns the result of applying the italic character attribute to String Use Use in Form components, but only applicable to Unifields. Description The function $italic returns the result of applying the italic character attribute to String . The result is visible only in a displayed Unifield. MY_UNIFIELD = $italic(\"aaabbb\") Copy Afterwards, MY_UNIFIELD contains aaabbb. Related Links stripattributes Remove character attributes, frames, and rulers from Source and put the result in Target. $stripattributes Return the result of removing character attributes, frames, and rulers from a string. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}